{"tid":1790482,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"S11可能屌打2020所有手機","createTime":"2019-12-20T04:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T14:14:37.000Z","uid":58335,"like":12,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ecb9d26746082f8ab530724cf36557da1ca8c2a3","tid":1790482,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T04:29:49.000Z","msg":"866<br />\n遠攝鏡<br />\n1億像素<br />\n<br />\nSamsung Galaxy S11 傳遠攝鏡都是世界第一<br />\n<br />\nSamsung Galaxy S11 系列手機，有傳將於 2 月 18 日發表，網上亦已傳出多時，將會採用支援像素 9 合 1 技術的一億像素 ISOCELL Bright HM1 感光元件。在遠攝鏡頭上，近日亦有傳聞會採用不低於 4,800 萬像素的感光元件，令遠攝表現有長足進步。<br />\n<br />\n據消息指，Samsung Galaxy S11e、S11 及 S11 Pro 的遠攝鏡頭內，都會配備不低於 4,800 萬像素的感光元件，應可成為世界最高像素的遠攝手機。由於數碼變焦拍攝時，都是以圖片放大的方式進行，如遠攝鏡頭用高像素的感光元件，對數碼變焦的拍攝效果，應有不少提升。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近日應用不少 Samsung 技術的 vivo X30 系列手機，已率先應用了 3,200 萬像素 50mm 遠攝相機，可見 Samsung Galaxy S11 系列應用不低於 4,800 萬像素感光元件的傳聞，在技術上已不難做到，或許明年除了 Samsung 外，還有不少旗艦手機，應用高像素遠攝相機亦不足為奇。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：twitter<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dcfever.com/news/readnews.php?id=26832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Fnews%2Freadnews.php%3Fid%3D26832&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5StC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=300921bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcfever.com/news/readnews.php?id=26832</a>"},{"pid":"1d4986033a3b22d942486134f848e7db976dc54d","tid":1790482,"uid":27432,"like":27,"dislike":16,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:32:48.000Z","msg":"一日係ANDROID 一日都唔會屌打"},{"pid":"e98860107a31d655505574cc41022a65260dddde","tid":1790482,"uid":46718,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:38:21.000Z","msg":"你講依三樣嘢隨時下年全部大陸機都係咁嘅spec"},{"pid":"a161eb11f7228509d26272b59b16231015ecb09d","tid":1790482,"uid":59920,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:40:41.000Z","msg":"可以影土星<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/